note: Free People is a global network and cultivates a culture that reflects the global nature of our organization and whose goal is to live freely, who have a sense of people, the environment and wildlife. People who want to make a difference in their lives and participate in a global community project. Their interest is to protect our home planet and ultimately humanity and its survival.
